|  named.conf  |   /etc/named.conf            |      /etc/bind/named.conf     |
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|  zone file   |   /var/named/named.*         |      /var/cache/bind          |
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|  pid-file    |   /var/run/named/named.pid   |      /var/run/named/named.pid |
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|  exe         |   /etc/init.d/named          |      /etc/init.d/bind9        |
